<inglise> COUNCIL REGULATION (EC, ECSC, EURATOM) No 2762/98 of 17 December 1998 adjusting with effect from 1 July 1998 the remuneration and pensions of officials and other servants of the European Communities and the weightings applied thereto </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGU M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;, EST&Uuml;, EURATOM) nr 2762/98, millega kohandatakse alates 1. juulist 1998 Euroopa &uuml;henduste ametnike ja muude teenistujate t&ouml;&ouml;tasusid ja pensione ning nende suhtes kohaldatavaid paranduskoefitsiente 17. detsember 1998 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN UNION, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA LIIDU N&Otilde;UKOGU, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing a Single Council and a Single Commission of the European Communities, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &uuml;henduste &uuml;htse n&otilde;ukogu ja &uuml;htse komisjoni asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Protocol on the Privileges and Immunities of the European Communities, and in particular Article 13 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &uuml;henduste privileegide ja immuniteetide protokolli, eriti selle artiklit 13, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Staff Regulations of Officials and the Conditions of Employment of Other Servants of the European Communities laid down by Council Regulation (EEC, Euratom, ECSC) No 259/68 (1), as last amended by Regulation (EC, ECSC, Euratom) No 2594/98 (2) and in particular Articles 63, 64, 65, 65a and 82 of the Staff Regulations, Annex XI to the Staff Regulations, and Article 20, first paragraph, and Article 64 of the Conditions of Employment, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &uuml;henduste ametnike personalieeskirju ja nende &uuml;henduste muude teenistujate teenistustingimusi, mis on s&auml;testatud m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;, EURATOM, EST&Uuml;) nr 259/68, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;, EST&Uuml;, EURATOM) nr 2594/98, (2) eelk&otilde;ige personalieeskirjade artikleid 63, 64, 65, 65a ja 82, nende XI lisa ning teenistustingimuste artikli 20 esimest l&otilde;iku ja artiklit 64, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the proposal from the Commission, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni ettepanekut </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas a review of the remuneration of officials and other servants carried out on the basis of a report by the Commission has shown that the remuneration and pensions of officials and other servants of the Communities should be adjusted under the 1998 annual review; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: komisjoni aruande alusel toimunud ametnike ja muude teenistujate t&ouml;&ouml;tasude &uuml;mberhindamisel on selgunud, et 1998. aasta &uuml;mberhindamise k&auml;igus tuleks &uuml;henduse ametnike ja muude teenistujate t&ouml;&ouml;tasusid ja pensione kohandada; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in accordance with Annex XI to the Staff Regulations, the annual adjustment in respect of 1999 will entail the establishment before 31 December 1999 of new weightings with retroactive effect from 1 July 1999; </inglise>
<eesti> koosk&otilde;las personalieeskirjade XI lisaga m&auml;&auml;ratakse 1999. aastal toimuva iga-aastase kohandamise k&auml;igus enne 31. detsembrit 1999 kindlaks uued paranduskoefitsiendid, mida kohaldatakse tagasiulatuvalt alates 1. juulist 1999; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas these new weightings could lead to retroactive adjustments to remuneration and pensions (positive or negative) in respect of the period of 1999 for which payments have already been made on the basis of this Regulation; </inglise>
<eesti> uute paranduskoefitsientidega v&otilde;ivad kaasneda tagasiulatuvad (positiivsed v&otilde;i negatiivsed) kohandused 1999. aasta selle ajavahemiku t&ouml;&ouml;tasudes ja pensionides, mille eest v&auml;ljamaksed on k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse alusel juba tehtud; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas provision should therefore be made for the payment of arrears in the event of an upward adjustment as a result of these weightings or for the recovery of sums overpaid in the event of a downward adjustment for the period between the effective date and the date of entry into force of the Council's decision on the annual adjustment in respect of 1999; </inglise>
<eesti> seep&auml;rast tuleks ette n&auml;ha, et 1999. aastal tehtavaid iga-aastaseid kohandusi k&auml;sitleva n&otilde;ukogu otsuse kohaldamise algkuup&auml;eva ja j&otilde;ustumise kuup&auml;eva vahelises ajavahemikus tuleb paranduskoefitsientidest tulenevate positiivsete kohanduste puhul maksta need summad tagantj&auml;rele ning negatiivsete kohanduste puhul enammakstud summad tagasi maksta; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas provision should be made for the effects of any such recovery to be spread over a period of not more than twelve months following the date of entry into force of the Council's decision on the annual adjustment in respect of 1999, </inglise>
<eesti> tuleks ette n&auml;ha, et iga sellise tagasimakse m&otilde;ju jaotatakse maksimaalselt kaheteistk&uuml;mne kuu peale, mis j&auml;rgnevad 1999. aastal tehtavaid iga-aastaseid kohandusi k&auml;sitleva n&otilde;ukogu otsuse j&otilde;ustumisele, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
