<inglise> Article 8 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 8 </eesti>
<inglise> With effect from 1 July 1998, the allowances for shiftwork laid down in Article 1 of Council Regulation (ECSC, EEC, Euratom) No 300/76 (4) shall be BEF 11 640, BEF 17 569, BEF 19 210 and BEF 26 189. </inglise>
